description:
This is a follow on to a subset of SCR#2291.0, and represents a set of FPGA and Linux driver software that serves to enhance the Epiq Solutions Sidekiq line of products with very standard and well defined digital signal processing capabilities that are found on other such software defined radio hardware. This includes timed command support, sub-band tuners, and other generic DSP capabilities.
SAND2019-3719 M
name: Sidekiq DSP v. 0.4
